If we come here, we'll get scolded~ Big sister,
let's go home~
??? : Oh! Did you get scared? You're such a boy~

Because the pond here is really deep! It's
dangerous!

??? \C[22], you're such a scaredy-cat. As long as
you don't fall, everything will be fine. Look,
I'll find some fish for you.

Ah! Big sister! Look at that fish over there!
Isn't its color a bit unusual?

\C[22]???\C[0] Really, huh! You're amazing, XX!
Hmm... I also want to find one...

\C[22]??? Ah... ah... no... what should I do...
XX...! W-wait...

Onne...! Chaaan!!! Bububu...gaboo, ubooa! I don't
like it...! Ta...su...

What's happening, XX?! Noooooooo!! I don't like
itttttttt!!! Ahhhhhhhhhhhhh!!!

Ugh... it hurts... my head feels like it's going
to split...

Ugh... it hurts... my head feels like it's going
to split...

Ugh... This makes it... the fourth fragment of
memories... The fragment I just saw isn't me.
Probably, it belongs to someone completely
different...

The fragments of memories before that were about
what happened before I came here. The town of my
hometown, my house, the castle... and a magical
book called Grimoire...
I came here... to save someone...

This world is not real... it's all fictional. But
there are real humans who have wandered into this
place.

I have to find the person I need to save... I
can't go back.

I have a feeling that the answer is surely
somewhere in the demon's stronghold. I feel like
there is someone I need to save there, that's the
feeling I have.

First... let's report to Gilcho that we have
obtained the power of all the Lolimon leaders.
Then, let's decide our future actions.

perfect timing, let's hurry.
